5\/Conflict_Kitchen_storefront_Iranian.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>The case study of the <a href=\"http:\/\/beautifultrouble.org\/case\/conflict-kitchen\/\">Conflict Kitchen<\/a>\u00a0designed by <strong>Sydney Arndt<\/strong> and inspired by <a href=\"http:\/\/www.bellhooksinstitute.com\/#\/about\/\">bell hooks<\/a>, gives more detail about the underlying tactics and principles at play in the use of food as outreach.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>If you want to make a change to your local community or to support a national campaign, one common way to do this is to run an information or fundraising stall using food.\u00a0These activities are key tactics for many campaigns and good causes. As such, there are often support kits or online information that you [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":29,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[128,129,45],"tags":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v15.6.2 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/mcrblogs.co.uk\/edlab\/edlab-template-educational-fundraiser\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_GB\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"EdLab Spark: Run an Educational Food &amp; Fundraising Stall - EdLab MMU\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"If you want to make a change to your local community or to support a national campaign, one common way to do this is to run an information or fundraising stall using food.\u00a0These activities are key tactics for many campaigns and good causes. As such, there are often support kits or online information that you [&hellip;]\" \/>\n<m